Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.76,0:00:09.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,The countless flowers,\Nenveloped in light...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.84,0:00:20.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,...gaze at tomorrow\Nwith unwavering eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.36,0:00:39.35,Regular,,0,0,0,,Everyone wishes for me to be pure...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.35,0:00:46.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,...but what can I bring\Nwith me to the frayed skies?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.81,0:00:53.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,What I've made my own\Nby breaking off flowers in bloom...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.90,0:00:59.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,All such sinful things...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.56,0:01:07.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why did I stop making\Npromises with the future?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.04,0:01:14.31,Regular,,0,0,0,,Because even if I try\Nto run far from all the pain...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.31,0:01:21.05,Regular,,0,0,0,,...a cold wind rustles\Nmy hair... Don't you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.05,0:01:28.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,Where can I ever find the answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.05,0:01:32.18,Regular,,0,0,0,,Dominüra?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.12,0:01:37.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,You said you'd\Ndo it for me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.19,0:01:39.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Emerald Ri Majon.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.63,0:01:46.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Simouns are the\Nvehicles of the gods.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.75,0:01:47.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,They can't fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.17,0:01:51.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,But that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.84,0:01:53.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,...the Emerald Ri Majon!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.97,0:02:05.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Ruins
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.99,0:02:45.64,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hey, check that out\Nfor me, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.64,0:02:48.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,Adjust the oil pressure for\Nthe communication-wire ejectors!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.38,0:02:49.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,I need somebody to\Npull on this for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.98,0:02:52.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,So we're going to be\Nworking here again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.61,0:02:53.65,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.70,0:02:56.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,First off, I want you all\Nto thoroughly pinpoint...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.52,0:02:58.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,...the areas that sustained damage.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.54,0:02:59.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,Right! We're already on it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.37,0:03:05.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,How is the old place?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.95,0:03:11.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.29,0:03:15.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,You look well. Glad to see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.84,0:03:16.87,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.87,0:03:17.92,Regular,,0,0,0,,Likewise.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.26,0:03:22.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,We just got back, and things\Nare already hectic, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.94,0:03:26.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, we were told to put a\Nrush on the Simoun repairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.15,0:03:27.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.35,0:03:32.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,Um.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.32,0:03:33.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.23,0:03:34.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.48,0:03:37.19,Regular,,0,0,0,,I need you to take\Na look at the lift.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.19,0:03:38.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.15,0:03:40.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.24,0:03:41.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,Please excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.28,0:03:42.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.29,0:03:55.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,Now that Shoukoku and the\Nhighlands have formed an alliance...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.00,0:04:00.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,...it's only a matter of\Ntime before they attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.94,0:04:06.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,Meaning we'll have to ask the sibyllae\Nagain to carry out such a cruel task.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.49,0:04:08.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's not a request.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.26,0:04:10.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's an order, Guragief.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.35,0:04:19.95,Regular,,0,0,0,,All of this happened\Nbecause of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.69,0:04:22.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,All because of\Nmy own selfishness!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.09,0:04:27.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,To think that I could ever forget\NAmuria and the Emerald Ri Majon...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.83,0:04:31.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,How could you have\Nbeen so naïve, Neviril?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.55,0:04:54.85,Regular,,0,0,0,,There are so many things that\Nmust never be forgotten, Neviril!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.05,0:05:19.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,Dominüra and Rimone...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.28,0:05:22.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,They vanished, didn't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.29,0:05:27.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Emerald Ri Majon...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.43,0:05:29.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,...failed, I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.52,0:05:39.10,Regular,,0,0,0,,Or maybe what really happened\Nwas that they copped out!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.87,0:05:42.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,If that were true, it would at\Nleast offer some consolation.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.40,0:05:47.64,Regular,,0,0,0,,No. What matters is not\Nthe cause but the result.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.31,0:05:51.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,For once again, we have lost\Nprecious comrades of ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.72,0:06:04.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,We've come home to the\NArcus Prima, haven't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.06,0:06:07.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,How can you be so\Ncavalier about this, Floe?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.83,0:06:11.64,Regular,,0,0,0,,Then are you saying that you're\Nnot glad to be back, Alty?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.64,0:06:12.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,Of course I'm glad!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.34,0:06:15.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sure I'm glad, but still...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.51,0:06:20.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,Come on, we're going to\Nbe roommates, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.60,0:06:22.21,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let's try to get along.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.11,0:06:24.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,I guess you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.17,0:06:45.83,Regular,,0,0,0,,Welcome back, everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.23,0:06:48.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,...to the Arcus Prima!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.97,0:06:53.22,Regular,,0,0,0,,I know that you have all gone through\Nmany changes during this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.22,0:06:54.11,Regular,,0,0,0,,...and we are most...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.11,0:06:56.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,The center was destroyed in the attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.38,0:07:01.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,As for the 12 Simouns belonging\Nto Chor Rubor and Chor Caput...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.20,0:07:03.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,...we had no choice but to abandon\Nany hopes of restoring them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.63,0:07:04.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,At this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.73,0:07:07.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,...the only chor remaining\Non the Arcus Prima...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.57,0:07:10.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,...is your own, Chor Tempest.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.57,0:07:12.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,High Priestess.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.03,0:07:14.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,What has become of the members\Nof Chor Rubor and Chor Caput?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.58,0:07:17.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,Nearly all of the sibyllae\Nhave gone to the Spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.75,0:07:19.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,You mean you gave them the axe.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.66,0:07:21.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,Watch your mouth, Aer!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.37,0:07:23.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,Come on, you know it's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.27,0:07:26.39,Regular,,0,0,0,,If there are no Simouns\Nto fly, they don't need us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.39,0:07:27.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,Silence!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.48,0:07:38.31,Regular,,0,0,0,,Now then, there's somebody here\Nwho would like to meet with you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.66,0:07:45.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.90,0:07:56.95,Regular,,0,0,0,,Welcome home, Neviril.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.95,0:07:59.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,I have returned, Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.08,0:08:06.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,That goes for all of you\NChor Tempest sibyllae.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.06,0:08:08.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,We are happy that you\Nmade it back safely.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.82,0:08:09.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.45,0:08:12.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.34,0:08:13.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.49,0:08:18.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Rimone and Sibylla\NDominüra are no longer with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.03,0:08:20.10,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.30,0:08:24.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,We are now headed toward the Ruins.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.27,0:08:26.31,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Ruins?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.77,0:08:28.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why the Ruins?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.27,0:08:30.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,We all know it's\Nno simple matter to...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.07,0:08:32.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,You are correct, Sibylla Yun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.71,0:08:37.64,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Ruins happen to be the holiest\Nplace in all of Simulacrum Kyuukoku.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.21,0:08:39.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,Not to mention a forbidden area.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.99,0:08:42.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,However, it is imperative that...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.06,0:08:48.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,...we reach the Ruins before the\Nforces of Shoukoku and the highlands.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.01,0:08:56.05,Regular,,0,0,0,,By any chance...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.53,0:09:02.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, what is your\Nquestion, Sibylla Floe?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.60,0:09:05.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,By any chance, are you forcing us?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.08,0:09:10.86,Regular,,0,0,0,,The only ones in all of\NSimulacrum Kyuukoku...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.86,0:09:13.90,Regular,,0,0,0,,...who have the ability\Nto execute this strategy...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.90,0:09:15.82,Regular,,0,0,0,,This is not a request.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.49,0:09:20.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,You are all expected to participate\Nin this battle without exception.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.39,0:09:25.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,I guess this means we don't have the\Nright to go to the Spring anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.25,0:09:27.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.03,0:09:29.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,Most likely...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.33,0:09:33.05,Regular,,0,0,0,,...we have nowhere to escape to.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.40,0:09:36.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,The only thing we\Ncan do is move on.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.36,0:10:34.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,I never thought I'd get the opportunity\Nto speak with you like this again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.27,0:10:35.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.76,0:10:38.31,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril is no longer\Nthe daughter I knew...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.31,0:10:40.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,...who would do anything I'd ask of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.75,0:10:45.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,And so there is nothing\Nmore I can do for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.20,0:10:50.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,Oh, no. I am grateful that you took\Nme under your wing, Vice Chancellor.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.21,0:10:53.35,Regular,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.35,0:10:54.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.52,0:10:57.17,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's just that you seem\Nto be a changed person.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.30,0:11:00.35,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.71,0:11:26.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,We owe you our lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.43,0:11:30.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,If it hadn't been for the Arcus Prima,\Nthe Messis would have surely fallen.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.50,0:11:32.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,You have done well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.37,0:11:34.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness we were in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.06,0:11:35.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,But still, Captain...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.50,0:11:36.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.55,0:11:42.72,Regular,,0,0,0,,You entrusted me with 12 sibyllae,\Nand I failed to return them all to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.72,0:11:44.05,Regular,,0,0,0,,Please forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.05,0:11:45.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,Captain Wauf.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.47,0:11:46.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.68,0:11:49.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,A detailed report can wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.64,0:11:51.69,Regular,,0,0,0,,In your opinion...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.69,0:11:54.31,Regular,,0,0,0,,...are Sibylla Dominüra\Nand Sibylla Rimone...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.65,0:11:57.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,I believe that they are both alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.11,0:12:01.71,Regular,,0,0,0,,Then what exactly happened to them?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.35,0:12:04.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,That I don't know. However...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.36,0:12:09.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,Perhaps we will find the answer\Nto that question at the Ruins.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.98,0:12:33.35,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.35,0:12:34.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aer, quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.94,0:12:35.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.59,0:12:43.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,— Neviril.\N— What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.07,0:12:44.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,Oh... nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.70,0:12:46.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,Para-sama! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.82,0:13:16.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,I know this is hardest on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.85,0:13:18.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.66,0:13:22.44,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm not the one who\Nhas to suffer the most.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.77,0:14:02.83,Regular,,0,0,0,,Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.58,0:14:11.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,As planned...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.96,0:14:14.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,...with communication cables\Nintact, Chor Tempest...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.62,0:14:16.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,...will descend as low as possible...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.80,0:14:21.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,...and protect the Ruins from attack\Nby the Shoukoku-highland forces.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.66,0:14:57.87,Regular,,0,0,0,,So these are the Ruins.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.49,0:14:59.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.62,0:15:01.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,This is my first time here as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.37,0:15:04.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,This is Tempus Spatium's holy land.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.88,0:15:07.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,I don't think the enemy\Nis here yet, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.63,0:15:09.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,Don't let your guard down!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.34,0:15:11.22,Regular,,0,0,0,,Oh, don't be so bossy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.22,0:15:12.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,Two o'clock!
Comment: 0,0:15:12.39,0:15:13.17,Regular,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.90,0:15:23.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.85,0:15:25.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,Could those be Simouns?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.36,0:15:30.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,But I've never seen\Nanything like them before!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.32,0:15:31.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,Nor have I!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.36,0:15:33.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,What should we do, Para-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.45,0:15:36.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,Para-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.49,0:15:37.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,Go after them!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.37,0:15:38.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.25,0:15:43.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,We'll take the one on the left!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.25,0:15:44.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.35,0:15:57.39,Regular,,0,0,0,,Are they planning to attack?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.90,0:16:07.65,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Shark Ri Majon?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.65,0:16:08.86,Regular,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.20,0:16:14.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,The enemy?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.90,0:16:18.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hurry, go after them, Para-sama!\NWe can't let them get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.02,0:16:20.83,Regular,,0,0,0,,Who are they? Who's\Noperating those Simouns?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.41,0:16:23.83,Regular,,0,0,0,,Who's flying those Simouns\Nto pray to the skies?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.61,0:16:25.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.55,0:16:28.59,Regular,,0,0,0,,How can they\Npossibly fly like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.26,0:16:36.44,Regular,,0,0,0,,Enemies... Is that the enemy?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.44,0:16:38.01,Regular,,0,0,0,,I won't let them get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.22,0:16:40.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,They're firing at us!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.56,0:16:41.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm not afraid!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.98,0:16:47.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,B-But, how could those\NSimouns be enemies of ours?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.73,0:16:49.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let's worry about that later, Floe!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.49,0:16:55.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aer?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.08,0:16:57.79,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aer, what do you\Nthink you're doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.79,0:16:58.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.95,0:17:00.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aer!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.32,0:17:05.10,Regular,,0,0,0,,Leave the pursuit to the others.\NLet's see what's inside those Ruins.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.10,0:17:06.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.13,0:17:07.59,Regular,,0,0,0,,What on earth are\Nyou talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.16,0:17:09.79,Regular,,0,0,0,,My music box...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.79,0:17:11.18,Regular,,0,0,0,,...it's playing now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.13,0:17:15.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's closed, but\Nit's still playing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.76,0:17:17.83,Regular,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.76,0:17:48.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,They managed to get away.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.33,0:17:50.79,Regular,,0,0,0,,What should we do now, Para-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.96,0:17:53.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,Head back to the Ruins.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.01,0:18:00.10,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hey, it stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.38,0:18:02.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,Come on, let's go, Aer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.89,0:18:04.31,Regular,,0,0,0,,H-Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.31,0:18:05.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hold on a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.73,0:18:08.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,How come you're acting\Nlike this all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.32,0:18:16.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,But this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.99,0:18:18.82,Regular,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Neviril?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.83,0:18:25.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,They think they're gonna get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.58,0:18:26.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,Not if I have my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.25,0:18:32.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,Huh? What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.63,0:18:36.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.91,0:19:01.95,Regular,,0,0,0,,I hit it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.45,0:19:06.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,Just one down after all that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.63,0:19:17.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,Onasia!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.42,0:19:20.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,Onasia...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.43,0:19:23.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,I am glad that you're here...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.63,0:19:25.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,...Sibylla Neviril...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.79,0:19:28.14,Regular,,0,0,0,,...Sibylla Aer...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.73,0:19:29.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,But why...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.60,0:19:32.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,...why are you here, Onasia?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.23,0:19:34.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Neviril...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.44,0:19:37.82,Regular,,0,0,0,,...I happen to be everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.82,0:19:40.90,Regular,,0,0,0,,And yet nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.24,0:19:45.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,Can't catch up...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.28,0:19:48.12,Regular,,0,0,0,,Who in the world\Nis flying that thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.12,0:19:49.95,Regular,,0,0,0,,Good question.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.95,0:19:52.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,And besides, there's something\Nnot right about this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.62,0:19:53.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let's go back!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.08,0:19:55.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.14,0:20:12.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,Onasia, how can...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.48,0:20:14.65,Regular,,0,0,0,,...this place be exactly\Nthe same as the Spring?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.19,0:20:18.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,Tempus watches over\Nthe flow of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.48,0:20:22.64,Regular,,0,0,0,,While Spatium shows us\Nmankind's rightful place.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.20,0:20:24.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,And when these two become a pair...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.75,0:20:29.65,Regular,,0,0,0,,...they bestow boundless\Nblessings and fear to the people.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.13,0:20:38.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yun?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.67,0:20:43.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.80,0:20:44.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,A Simoun?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.86,0:20:58.92,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yun!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.22,0:21:01.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yun, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.11,0:21:06.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,This place... What exactly\Nis going on in this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.54,0:21:12.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yun!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.58,0:21:13.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yun!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.43,0:21:15.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,Here in the Ruins...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.67,0:21:18.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,...time and space...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.54,0:21:24.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,...are released from all curses.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.85,0:21:39.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hold on a second, Yun.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.56,0:21:41.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,Just what was going on back there?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.93,0:21:42.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,They're all...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.82,0:21:45.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,...waiting for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.60,0:21:47.79,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.44,0:21:49.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,I know what's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.14,0:21:52.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,This isn't just some place\Nthat looks like the Spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.20,0:21:54.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.25,0:21:55.87,Regular,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, Aer?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.68,0:21:58.08,Regular,,0,0,0,,This place is...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.08,0:22:00.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,...the Spring itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.15,0:22:02.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's just like Grandpa said!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.19,0:22:19.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,Anglas!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.86,0:22:30.11,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aer!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.19,0:22:47.90,Regular,,0,0,0,,It is played by my wounds...\Nthe song of prayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.90,0:22:52.14,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let it ring out over\Nthe grieving universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.14,0:22:59.21,Regular,,0,0,0,,Can we change tomorrow?\NDon't be afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.21,0:23:06.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,I want to let you know\Nhow my heart's overflowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.62,0:23:19.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,I want to get closer to you.\NI want to feel your pulse.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.70,0:23:24.87,Regular,,0,0,0,,I was too defiant,\Nand I took the long way around.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.87,0:23:28.85,Regular,,0,0,0,,The blue moon is swaying silently.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.85,0:23:32.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,My true heart's desire is you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.89,0:23:38.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,I can't reach you.\NMy tears of pain trickle down.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.75,0:23:44.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,Soar away into the\Nsky, song of prayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.30,0:23:47.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,Carrying my love that came too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.73,0:23:53.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,What can I do to change tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.40,0:23:59.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,Just hold on to "now" the way it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.00,0:24:06.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,To Be Continued
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.21,0:24:12.72,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aer and Mamina have been barred\Nfrom attending Anglas's funeral.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.55,0:24:15.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,Next time on Simoun...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.97,0:24:18.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Funeral.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.55,0:24:20.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Funeral
